messages.message: If the errors are stopping anything, please share them, so that we can debug.

BTW, those errors should really be warnings. I have a ticket to downgrade the message to a warning, and to fix the code that is generating the warnings in the first place. Ultimately, the reason these messages are printed is b/c the Python code is sending 0 usage for some LLM token usage metrics. This is correct, though if the usage is 0 then we should not send any metrics to license-service at all as an optimization.
